Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. At that point, I want to introduce Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Power to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a thumping. They're coming after me. Thump, thump. The thump, thumps almost got me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but they did not succeed because I have a will of iron. I iron my will all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we're very serious about things this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've greeted the people in my usual style of absurdity, which is the only sanity left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurdity is the only sanity left to mankind. So we're going to answer any questions people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,may have this morning. Is that what we're doing? I read that. You want to read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I thank you for your infinite love beyond the time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to be closer to the mic. A little bit closer to the mic, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We came from Korea. We came from Korea, South Korea. We have gone through a hard time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to get permission to come here. They had a hard time getting permission to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Because I am an army officer. Because what? He's an army officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. To come here, I have to obtain permission from my four bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so difficult and a complicated process. I intensely aspire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got to be closer to the mic. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I intensely aspire to attend. He's got to be closer to the mic, please. Your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult for him to come from Korea because he has four different bosses,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,basically, to get permission from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:04:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is thankful that he's able to get permission to come this time as well as he
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to know if it's in the highest good that he come, if possible, to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know what's in the highest good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If it serves the highest good for him to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little late to ask that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My asking is prayer, your prayer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to pray for him to be able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To continue to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To continue to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in his own highest good to be here, Jesus. And we pray for his welfare, O Lord. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to Korea, Susan and I, some years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it once or twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to Korea twice, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it takes too long to fly there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They were going to have supersonic jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they never got around to the supersonic jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought if they got around to supersonic jets,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we would fly there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And we had a wonderful time in Korea, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we loved the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know right now that Korean is under great stress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as it goes with North Korea,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so we appreciate very much that you were able to come to this panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a gift from me and my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Next questioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a picture with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for coming all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way from North Korea to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the Koreans, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we flew twice to Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Met with a lot of government people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she's going to read one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They already, because they speak very little English...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't speak much Korean, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,intensely prayed to dear Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to make me an instrument of the Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,my being,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I pray to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,your image comes to mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,then I can't differentiate God from you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to whom I pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your energy is closer to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,than even Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice rings in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am anxious without your picture in my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I devote my time to listen to your DVDs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and read your books as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay that I cherish you in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as God's image,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or am I idol-worshipping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God and Doc are totally separate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but his message is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a combination of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,self-realization of your own spiritual worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the messages are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The messages are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What messages?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you go ahead and answer it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she said she listens to your DVDs every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And she cannot distinguish between you and God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And is she idol-worshipping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, God really speaks to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only a matter of learning how to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,God speaks to all of us, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we learn how to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We walk through the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and we hear the birds singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're naive, you don't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that's God singing to you via the bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that presents itself to you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because nothing else but divinity exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All that exists is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you don't have to worry about finding God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,God's everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have to come to is the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that the essence of everything that exists is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing exists except God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we treat everything in life with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We treat everything and everyone with respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone and everything reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than God, what could there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-God?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:11:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing for my spiritual pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to test?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she wants a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.45,0:11:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless your courage for coming up in front of the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and speaking to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,May I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she wants a lollipop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want dessert on top of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very brave to come up in front of a whole audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question, and I just wanted to meet you and to come up and to say thank
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you for being a light in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what this microphone said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wants to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here in the world with the work that you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have much to say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God said, you're going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, okay, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We incarnate when divinity wills it, when it's God's will for us to become a human again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and we do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:13:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the world of the physical expression, when we're done with that, we retreat back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world of spirit, and then maybe reemerge later again in the world of the physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's up to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't obey God's will, uh-oh, you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And can I have a blessing from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is in regards to prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In one of your lectures, you talk about clearing things using intense prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering how one makes their prayers intense or how you make your prayers intense?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you talked about a clearing prayer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a clearing prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can minimize, I guess, through extensive prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So he says, how do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The clearing prayer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you say that you're intensely praying,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,how is that different than a regular prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a degree of intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to explain to people intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of energy and power that you give it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and you invoke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you invoke it in God's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,now and forever, amen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,then you are invoking it very, very strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the intensity of your devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of one's own personal energy tends to increase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To pray intensely, in a way, redoubles it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because in a way, all you're doing is reflecting back to God
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is divinity in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,which is manifesting as your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to first express my great gratitude to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of serenity since I've been coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with a potential university...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,my potential university education.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your potential university education?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You state that a true liberal education
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that the great books of the Western world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you read when you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the equivalent of going to college, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been accepted into a program
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,where the curriculum is great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At a small college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forget the name of that college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the name of the college?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's St. John's College.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, St. John's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Their curriculum is the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember calibrating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A calibrator is quite high, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess that's my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you speak extensively in your lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and books about the fall of academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spoken extensively about the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,lack of integrity in academia in today's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess my question is I feel drawn to this study
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I guess I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know if the integrity of the program is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At St. John's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At St. John's, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he wants to know if it's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The integrity...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this about St. John's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The integrity of their curriculum is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They follow the great books of the Western world, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates higher than Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates higher than Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that Harvard calibrates all that high, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard's got the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but this other college has the integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In healing and recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a chapter on death and dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And you describe one can use their imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to help those close to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, someone in the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or even yesterday in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you clarify how to do this process
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't know anyone specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would be using your imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In behalf of the people who are praying for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's full of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,People are praying for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you try to reinforce it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by collaborating with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,adding the energy of your own psyche
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to their intention
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase the effectiveness of their prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're praying in their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to be specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't know an individual,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any individuals in Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can pray on behalf of those who are suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and threatened for their peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my question is several years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in, I had a rebirthing session.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And my heart opened up like a flower so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt absolute, undescribable total peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You felt what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Total peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Indescribable peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a profound peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All over my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:21:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was residual.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It lasted for several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just wondering if I could have that calibrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What calibrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that event.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she have that event calibrated that she had?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That spiritual experience that I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate that event.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 500, 560, 580, 575.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very high level of love, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of like a peak at what could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, right.
