Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's the only, I mean, that was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what I experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wondered if I could receive the transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard people ask, and I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.17,0:22:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She wondered what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If she could receive the transmission,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which is what you get when you see the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the teacher, that's what you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is that silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's automatic, it's automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a silent transmission,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's what you get when you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's automatic, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I appreciate both of you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the community that you have, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people experience their birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,re-experience their own birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in graduate school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in graduate school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in graduate school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's something that's really been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's really bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.84,0:23:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it like a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a fact, or are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:23:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:23:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is bothering me, not something's bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.41,0:24:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have a learning disability.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.65,0:24:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She has what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She, I don't know if she has one or not, but she seems to think
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that she has a learning disability.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.38,0:24:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans have a learning disability.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd all be enlightened already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The average person is pretty dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.36,0:24:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch the evening news, you realize how dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.95,0:24:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she buzzed me off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.35,0:24:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.96,0:24:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
