Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.61,0:24:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.61,0:24:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What disability do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.61,0:25:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having a hard time learning higher math, understanding what my teacher is teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.11,0:25:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
