Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.22,0:25:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.22,0:25:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.22,0:25:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're going as far as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.22,0:25:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, higher math is really not your subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.98,0:25:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
