Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,okay thank you very much appreciate it at one time or another just about everybody's useful along the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.19,0:39:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,path you know what i mean my question is about parents i'm kind of curious if before we incarnate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.71,0:39:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on this life do we pick our parents or our family for the highest karmic undoing um when we come
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.38,0:40:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,before we come back into this life do we pick our parents for the highest karmic learning i don't
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.23,0:40:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,know i don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.44,0:40:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we pick our parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.82,0:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We do have a say in picking our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the spiritual levels are very determining.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.05,0:40:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.17,0:40:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.46,0:40:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.82,0:40:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That undoes a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.55,0:40:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have very spiritually committed parents, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.88,0:40:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely, very intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.15,0:40:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to church every Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.32,0:40:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.98,0:40:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we didn't eat any meat during Lent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.92,0:40:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less on Good Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.59,0:40:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ate meat on Good Friday, you'd probably go to hell, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.07,0:41:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.48,0:41:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had many high experiences in my lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.80,0:41:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.51,0:41:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.96,0:41:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Had abusive parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.73,0:41:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ironic on that last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.17,0:41:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.13,0:41:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.15,0:41:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ended up marrying a woman much like an emotional abusive mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.51,0:41:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Much like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.96,0:41:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotional abusive mother that he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.65,0:41:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.48,0:41:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.23,0:41:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyhow, it's not my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.92,0:41:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionally abusive?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.82,0:41:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.69,0:41:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.40,0:41:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.90,0:41:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.23,0:41:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dumb guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.88,0:41:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.19,0:41:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.94,0:41:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.23,0:41:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.36,0:41:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That ended up in divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.63,0:41:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.42,0:41:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.19,0:42:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the propensity is that I got in trouble a lot as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.17,0:42:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always had that feeling of going to the principal's office in the pit of my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.01,0:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems such a paradox to have really high experiences and a wonderful relationship with divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.84,0:42:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of a sudden, you just feel in your gut that...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.34,0:42:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.84,0:42:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding this is certainly ego attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.23,0:42:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't figure out how to unlock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.69,0:42:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How to...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.38,0:42:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrendered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.26,0:42:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.82,0:42:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that other people have hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.00,0:43:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I guess it's starting to come clear that am I angry at myself for walking into this situation and allowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.69,0:43:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Things...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.07,0:43:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery still to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.67,0:43:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.80,0:43:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.46,0:43:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.63,0:43:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.65,0:43:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life gets screwed up periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.53,0:43:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.25,0:43:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That applies to everybody on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.03,0:43:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.55,0:43:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.19,0:43:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.07,0:43:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.21,0:43:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.88,0:43:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.92,0:43:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.36,0:43:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.44,0:43:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I knew what I was going to ask you when I was over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.59,0:43:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm really confused right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.84,0:43:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.17,0:43:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.15,0:43:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.61,0:43:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fearful of...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.28,0:43:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of getting everybody's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.17,0:43:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, rather than just standing up for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.05,0:43:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.76,0:43:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.94,0:43:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.80,0:43:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.28,0:43:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you bring a third party in, you're adding to the confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.84,0:43:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Their opinion, their attitude, their approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.03,0:43:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.53,0:43:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to let go wanting other people's approval in order to get your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.80,0:43:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.46,0:43:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're wanting everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.80,0:44:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's approval, then you haven't achieved your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.40,0:44:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When you become independent of other people's opinions, it doesn't mean to become ignorant
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.69,0:44:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.69,0:44:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.69,0:44:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people become clumsy and stupid, and it'd be better that they stayed in bed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.17,0:44:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.11,0:44:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.11,0:44:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.11,0:44:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.11,0:44:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.11,0:44:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you need to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.11,0:44:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.11,0:44:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.11,0:44:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.11,0:44:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They were...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.11,0:44:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.11,0:44:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know that they were even doing their best, but you have to forgive them for
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.11,0:44:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.11,0:44:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.55,0:44:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.55,0:44:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.48,0:44:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.48,0:44:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to soft-soap it, but it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.48,0:44:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if they really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You really were miserable, then they weren't doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.03,0:44:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need to just forgive them and put it in the past and realize that you're destined
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.19,0:44:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.19,0:44:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.19,0:44:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.32,0:44:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to let go of that, because that's holding you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.36,0:45:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Every now and then, there's an occasional zinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.07,0:45:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a couple months ago, my mom threw a grenade in my lap, and she's so disappointed at the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.57,0:45:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,way I turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.57,0:45:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.21,0:45:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His mom threw a grenade in his lap, because she was disappointed on the way he turned
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.55,0:45:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.55,0:45:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.55,0:45:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.57,0:45:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need to forgive him and walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.21,0:45:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.21,0:45:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.21,0:45:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.21,0:45:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.21,0:45:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.21,0:45:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.21,0:45:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.21,0:45:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.21,0:45:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's nice if your mother can be proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.21,0:45:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.38,0:45:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I always worked for my mother's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.38,0:45:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I always got her approval, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.00,0:45:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did what she approved of.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.00,0:45:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.00,0:45:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.00,0:45:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.86,0:45:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.86,0:45:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.07,0:46:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you very much for being here with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.07,0:46:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have recently been dealing with a sarcoma cancer issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.53,0:46:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to speak slowly, and then the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.48,0:46:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You recently have what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.15,0:46:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have recently been dealing with a sarcoma cancer issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.50,0:46:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A cancer issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.21,0:46:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.46,0:46:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.46,0:46:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been dealing with cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.46,0:46:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.46,0:46:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have accepted that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.94,0:46:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as my karma
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.88,0:46:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have accepted that as my karma
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.36,0:46:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand from your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.01,0:46:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that at some level
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.32,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have attracted this to me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.76,0:46:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand from your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.09,0:46:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that I may have attracted this to me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.23,0:46:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,well attraction is not exactly the right word
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.05,0:46:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,created it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.67,0:47:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,occasioned it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.03,0:47:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so getting any kind of an illness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.59,0:47:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,could have a karmic antecedent
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.19,0:47:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that is true
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.55,0:47:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so if that is true
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.57,0:47:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.40,0:47:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how does one not attract illness to them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.76,0:47:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not the right wording attract
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.90,0:47:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you make it sound like a bug flying around
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.80,0:47:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and you attract the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.51,0:47:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you attract the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.57,0:47:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and you attract the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.59,0:47:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and he lands on your arm
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.71,0:47:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you avoid the consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.17,0:47:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of having bad karma
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.59,0:47:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is really what she is saying
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.36,0:47:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,well what you do is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.80,0:47:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to create as much good
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.36,0:47:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,karma for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.40,0:47:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can to counterbalance it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.65,0:47:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to counterbalance it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.98,0:47:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to compensate for it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.90,0:47:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,by as much
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.69,0:48:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.01,0:48:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.42,0:48:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.42,0:48:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest is up to God
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.80,0:48:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.86,0:48:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,yes thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.86,0:48:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.86,0:48:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.84,0:48:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and stay out of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.57,0:48:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.42,0:48:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.42,0:48:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I also have a gift for you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.42,0:48:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.15,0:49:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.76,0:49:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a desire to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.76,0:49:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.76,0:49:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am thankful for God that I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.98,0:49:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thankful for God that I am here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.84,0:49:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have had that opportunity today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.84,0:49:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just ask your blessings on my life
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.90,0:49:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he just wanted to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.13,0:49:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.13,0:49:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on opening the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.13,0:49:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and your blessings on opening
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.13,0:49:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart up
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.13,0:49:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,oh God bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.13,0:49:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.23,0:49:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,kaboom
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.23,0:49:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,can I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.23,0:49:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sure come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.23,0:49:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,now he wants my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.23,0:49:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,good God what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.05,0:49:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.05,0:49:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you guys for your dedication and willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.59,0:50:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from China.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.38,0:50:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now the government lacks transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.98,0:50:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.98,0:50:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The government lacks transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.17,0:50:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Transparency and-
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.17,0:50:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In China?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.38,0:50:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.38,0:50:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.38,0:50:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.38,0:50:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the media is blocked and controlled by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.07,0:50:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So democracy is a really big issue there, and it's influencing all the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.61,0:50:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, as a citizen and simply a human being, what can I do to improve the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.78,0:50:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.51,0:50:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Improve the situation where?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.05,0:50:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In China, because they're blocking all the media and the internet, they only allow certain
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.63,0:50:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,things to come into China, and it has to do with the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.84,0:50:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a person-
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.84,0:50:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Has to do with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.84,0:50:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it has to do with the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.80,0:50:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The politics of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.80,0:50:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.80,0:50:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.80,0:50:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.80,0:51:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So as an individual, what could he do that would change this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.94,0:51:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't advise trying to change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.98,0:51:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.98,0:51:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not unless you're willing to die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.71,0:51:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.71,0:51:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.71,0:51:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.71,0:51:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was the emperor of China and you came to me with that, I would ask them to remove
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.23,0:51:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,your head promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.05,0:51:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a disrespect for authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.05,0:51:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.36,0:51:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See, in a certain culture, authority necessitates respect, and it's not up to you to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.15,0:51:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,who deserves it, who deserves respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.19,0:51:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.26,0:51:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The king is the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.73,0:51:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's a bad king, he's still the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.51,0:51:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sovereign is still the sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.01,0:51:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to respect the position of the sovereign and ignore the personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.38,0:51:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.17,0:51:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the great kings of history were terrible people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.05,0:52:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But they were still king, whether you liked it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.40,0:52:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.40,0:52:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So we cannot pick or choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.65,0:52:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that this could be turned around by prayer, or ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.80,0:52:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What turned around?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.80,0:52:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the situation that the government is blocking all outside information ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.05,0:52:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.15,0:52:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So he just has to know that this is the way it is, and that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.09,0:52:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.09,0:52:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.09,0:52:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.09,0:52:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But people will ... democracy will still be insufficient in China, keep being like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.96,0:52:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It might change, but it's going to take a while before China gets caught up with the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.34,0:52:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.34,0:52:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It might change tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.65,0:52:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.65,0:52:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.65,0:52:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, all kinds of situations change.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.23,0:52:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You get idealistic about how a country should behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.63,0:52:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do about overpopulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.73,0:52:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.73,0:52:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.86,0:52:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass a law.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.86,0:53:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.86,0:53:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No more babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.86,0:53:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,China allows you one baby, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.86,0:53:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.86,0:53:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're allowed one baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.86,0:53:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I marry a single child from the family, I'm allowed to have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.86,0:53:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.86,0:53:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.86,0:53:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I read your book, The Truth Versus Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.86,0:53:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In that book, you ... the China ... Chinese government is calibrated in 190, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.86,0:53:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is ...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.86,0:53:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.86,0:53:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.86,0:53:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.86,0:53:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.86,0:53:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.86,0:53:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.86,0:53:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.86,0:53:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.86,0:53:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.86,0:53:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.86,0:53:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.86,0:53:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.86,0:53:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.86,0:53:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.86,0:53:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.86,0:53:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.86,0:53:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.86,0:53:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.86,0:53:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.86,0:53:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.86,0:53:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.86,0:53:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.86,0:53:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.86,0:53:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you calibrate right now the Chinese government?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.50,0:53:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Chinese government ... We have permission to do Chinese government
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.82,0:53:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.94,0:53:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 190, 195, 200, 199, 198, 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.63,0:53:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese government has come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.73,0:53:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.73,0:53:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.73,0:53:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.73,0:53:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still ... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.73,0:54:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is looking like it is going towards change.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.69,0:54:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just gonna take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.69,0:54:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's just going to take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.86,0:54:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a citizen, I can only accept the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.86,0:54:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your opinion. That's your advice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.34,0:54:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, China has been like it has been for many, many, many, many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.44,0:54:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world around it has changed, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.09,0:54:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,while China still remains as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.38,0:54:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'll take a while before the change will come up and take over,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.67,0:54:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will eventually come.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.05,0:54:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, in a democracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.51,0:54:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the head of the country changes all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.61,0:54:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This person's here for four years,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.15,0:54:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then he goes out and somebody else comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.80,0:54:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's constantly changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.71,0:54:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.44,0:54:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to think what the politics were in China when I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.21,0:54:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in China a couple of times
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.30,0:54:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to remember what the politics was at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.19,0:55:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you can't have more than one child, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.73,0:55:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you marry someone that's a single.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.42,0:55:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A single child, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.57,0:55:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.28,0:55:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, the rulers do what they can with the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.98,0:55:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when the situation changes, they must change, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.80,0:55:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a citizen, I just await the situation change?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.88,0:55:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.69,0:55:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk about it, but, yeah, you have to wait for it to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.23,0:55:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you, Doctor. Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.28,0:55:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved China when I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.11,0:55:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.30,0:55:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.36,0:55:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.80,0:55:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, great food, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.32,0:55:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All the restaurants were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.98,0:55:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.53,0:55:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.23,0:56:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you and ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.38,0:56:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.71,0:56:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.01,0:56:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.46,0:56:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.80,0:56:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.11,0:56:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.88,0:56:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.76,0:56:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.44,0:56:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.96,0:56:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.03,0:56:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.44,0:56:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could please expand on fulfilling your potential a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.19,0:56:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because I am confused sometimes between working too much as a part of my function here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.36,0:56:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and wasting time for spiritual progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.98,0:56:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to talk about one's potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.15,0:57:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels like he devotes a lot of time to...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.40,0:57:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to work, and that, you know, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.67,0:57:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us do that, and there's very little time left over for spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.40,0:57:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.92,0:57:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the balance, you know, sometimes we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.09,0:57:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the wrong way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.94,0:57:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.92,0:57:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.46,0:57:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual is an inner attitude, and nothing can interrupt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.26,0:57:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with work, because to be in a certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.42,0:57:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,attitude or way with life, it doesn't depend on what's going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.32,0:57:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To be appreciative of life in all of its expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.98,0:57:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to be grateful for life in all of its expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.44,0:57:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,does not put any requirements on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.26,0:57:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It puts the requirement on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.71,0:58:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be happy whether it's raining or whether the sun is shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.17,0:58:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say, well, I'm only going to be happy when the sun shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.15,0:58:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.03,0:58:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see that all the weather is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.53,0:58:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a rainy day this morning, you say, well, wow, it's raining today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.13,0:58:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's sunny, you say, oh, wow, it's a sunny day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.07,0:58:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's snowing, you say, hey, look, it's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.80,0:58:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.13,0:58:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.21,0:58:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he home?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.34,0:58:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.69,0:58:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.07,0:58:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This week, a week ago, we had a very exciting morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.23,0:58:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We got up, and Susan said, it's snowing outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.76,0:58:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.36,0:58:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I jump all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.36,0:58:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live in Arizona, if it's snowing, it's a big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.03,0:58:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live in New York, snowing is not a big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.61,0:59:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So context decides the significance and meaning of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.07,0:59:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.28,0:59:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's snow where and when and under what circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.00,0:59:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you've had a whole winter of snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.01,0:59:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that it's snowing today is not exactly good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.59,0:59:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what I mean by context.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.15,0:59:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So the significance of many things in our life,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.11,0:59:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, very dependent on context to whom it's happening and when
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.26,0:59:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and in what kind of a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.55,0:59:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As a woman will say, to be pregnant at a certain time and month in her life was fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.61,0:59:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If it had happened under different circumstances, she'd think of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.11,0:59:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.65,0:59:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.21,0:59:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.19,0:59:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.94,0:59:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.30,0:59:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.94,0:59:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So circumstances contribute to the meaning, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.51,1:00:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to take a quick break, about 15 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.90,1:00:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll come back and finish questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.50,1:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.88,1:00:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.46,1:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to get them to say bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.88,1:00:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.80,1:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Our bird says bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.51,1:00:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All the police, I think I'm being kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.65,1:00:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.01,1:00:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.48,1:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks for their presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.92,1:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.17,1:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.36,1:01:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for beautiful work, and you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.75,1:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in Thailand at a monastery for about 150 days, where I want to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.25,1:01:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to speak slower and right into the mic.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.57,1:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in Thailand?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.36,1:01:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In an Indiana Buddhist center, monastery, where I want to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.17,1:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had difficulties with negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.61,1:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.09,1:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Difficulties with negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.32,1:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.76,1:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean by negative entities?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.19,1:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative thoughts or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.71,1:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.30,1:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes true, and then I couldn't do my thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.80,1:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I really want to go to reach enlightenment, but it threw my mind, and I didn't reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.38,1:02:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.84,1:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you have any?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.80,1:02:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any, I don't know, answer for it, or?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.38,1:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He really felt like he applied himself to reach enlightenment, but it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.34,1:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't reach it, so is there any?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.61,1:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he think he was going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.01,1:02:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get enlightened between Monday and Friday, or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.96,1:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You got another 50 years to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.09,1:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.67,1:02:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what you do is you state your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.63,1:02:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.26,1:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you surrender it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.38,1:02:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't keep trying to control it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.05,1:02:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.42,1:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask God to reach enlightenment, it's now up to God, not up to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.15,1:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's slated to happen, then it will happen, and nothing can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.71,1:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not slated to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.61,1:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.07,1:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.03,1:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Except that you will end up at death as a frustrated devotee.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.75,1:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.15,1:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to have some kind of karma in the next lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.36,1:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So to die in this lifetime, a frustrated devotee.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.42,1:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably would have a very good God will feel sorry for you, and you get reborn in Zen Monastery or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.07,1:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.07,1:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.19,1:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering it to God means surrendering it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.59,1:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.94,1:04:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're meant to be enlightened, then it will come about no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.07,1:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires several things.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.25,1:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One is karmic propensity, infinite divine mercy, and many other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.92,1:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.92,1:04:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And many other factors of which we do not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.96,1:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes on, it is very sudden and very unexpected and very profound, profoundly changes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.80,1:04:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.19,1:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What everything looks like, what it seems to be, what its reality is, all changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.80,1:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.80,1:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And once it's changed, so you can see from a changed viewpoint, then you're not being
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.21,1:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.05,1:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.00,1:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.00,1:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about being frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.00,1:04:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.07,1:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.07,1:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.98,1:05:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Being frustrated means that you're, you know, not surrendering to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.98,1:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God's will is things happen by karmic propensities, plus God's will, plus many circumstances of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.15,1:05:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have no awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.15,1:05:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.15,1:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's the willingness that counts more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.86,1:05:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.86,1:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.86,1:05:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.86,1:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.03,1:05:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.03,1:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.03,1:05:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.03,1:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.71,1:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.71,1:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.71,1:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.71,1:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.84,1:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.84,1:05:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.03,1:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.76,1:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.76,1:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.76,1:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.76,1:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.76,1:05:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.71,1:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.71,1:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I'm very blessed to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.23,1:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told six months ago that I would meet my teacher that I have studied with in past
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.07,1:06:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,lives, and I knew it was you, and I'm very blessed that you are here in my life and in
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.19,1:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.40,1:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.40,1:06:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask what's on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.84,1:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am that teacher. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.82,1:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.28,1:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You look familiar from a couple thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.57,1:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you from Fum Boo, the year 2012.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.55,1:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, no, I'm glad you've returned.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.61,1:06:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.38,1:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.50,1:06:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about choiceless awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.90,1:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Choices and awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.92,1:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Choiceless.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.98,1:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Choiceless awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.19,1:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Choiceless awareness. What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.30,1:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That means once you're in that state of presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.05,1:07:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,when you are so imbued in the presence of presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.92,1:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's no choiceless.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.19,1:07:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything just flows and just happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.34,1:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've spoken so beautifully about it many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.69,1:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in that state...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.36,1:07:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always in that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.53,1:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always in that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.73,1:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So where does...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.65,1:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.40,1:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.01,1:07:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.96,1:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is flowing perfectly with ultimate beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.71,1:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and perfection right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.92,1:07:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.17,1:07:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.13,1:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.32,1:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So where does choice fit in then?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.69,1:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.55,1:07:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go back and forth with just being in that choiceless state,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.63,1:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the dualistic choice kicks in.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.90,1:08:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, there's what you're thinking about at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.67,1:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's what your life is really about.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.07,1:08:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't think every moment about what our life is really about,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.32,1:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because you'd never get a chance to live it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.09,1:08:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend all your time thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.10,1:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So we make our choice, you know, to visit China, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.35,1:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that only takes one second to make the choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.97,1:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to think about it on the plane all the way to China,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.10,1:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.68,1:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm choosing to go to China and say, repeat that over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.96,1:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've already made a choice,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.22,1:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's sent your life in this direction rather than this direction, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.15,1:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.64,1:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.80,1:08:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're overcome by evil, your life is fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.03,1:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.93,1:09:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be a hand on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.25,1:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, now it's official.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.69,1:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, she could be right and I could be wrong, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.85,1:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to heaven, and God says,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.36,1:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,how come you didn't put your hand on that lady's head?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.90,1:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Send me back to Chicago for a lifer.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.18,1:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.48,1:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.27,1:09:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.05,1:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to give you a copy of my master's thesis in divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.55,1:09:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,where I extensively cited your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.17,1:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.86,1:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brilliant work.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.06,1:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.78,1:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to ask you if you would please calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.14,1:09:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate the work?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.22,1:09:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.89,1:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I have permission to calibrate the thesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.84,1:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 450, 470, 480, 490.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.98,1:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,500.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.73,1:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right at 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.64,1:10:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.61,1:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.19,1:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.42,1:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could ask for more?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.53,1:10:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.07,1:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.84,1:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful to be here, and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.39,1:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the value of perseverance.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.67,1:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In my work, I have a company that's developing small airplanes, small jets,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.28,1:10:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and it appears to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.98,1:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm financially failing, and I have a dilemma of how to know when to move on to something else,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.82,1:10:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,or what the value of it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.28,1:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.72,1:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't be in too bad shape if you've got a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.15,1:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, having a choice is a blessing, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.76,1:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the choice about?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.22,1:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to persevere with it indefinitely, or to let go and move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.10,1:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what you mean, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.00,1:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.10,1:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.84,1:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Other ventures and other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.11,1:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to ask the arm?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.60,1:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I would appreciate that very much, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.85,1:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in his, I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.11,1:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in his best interest to persevere with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.13,1:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.10,1:11:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he resume it at a different date?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.05,1:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may be the wrong time, the wrong company, the wrong financing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.51,1:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a thousand factors.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.85,1:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could maybe at a later date?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.56,1:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, should he be, it might be appropriate to return to the same endeavor at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.92,1:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this, oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.31,1:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.38,1:11:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, well, you got it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.02,1:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.07,1:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.18,1:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take your hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.26,1:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.35,1:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.14,1:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the timing may be off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.64,1:11:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.40,1:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.39,1:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.06,1:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.53,1:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up wanting things from God for Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.78,1:12:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.63,1:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave up wanting things from God for Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.22,1:12:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting things from God?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.98,1:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.90,1:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.17,1:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.90,1:12:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.39,1:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, what if you got them anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.19,1:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.86,1:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, instead of, well, I'm praying for God's will instead of praying for what.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.48,1:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you mean, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.32,1:12:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I want his will for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.14,1:12:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.28,1:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.01,1:12:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and when I pray in the morning, when I pray in the morning, I pray what is thy will,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.35,1:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and how can I?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.03,1:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be your servant today?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.50,1:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.97,1:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And most often, I just, it's silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.27,1:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.85,1:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how to know which way to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.10,1:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband said, if you surrender to every moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.32,1:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.09,1:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then that's being in God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.51,1:13:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.50,1:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.75,1:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.02,1:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is, is, and we have to assume,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.06,1:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that divinity is the source.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.30,1:13:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Without divinity, you and I wouldn't be speaking here at this table,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.57,1:13:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,nor would Susan be sitting here, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.10,1:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So the whole phenomena is a product of multiple composites.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.28,1:13:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.76,1:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And we add our two cents worth in at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.19,1:14:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And let it be a blue Cadillac, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.21,1:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.84,1:14:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.11,1:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is a mercer to these bands.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.98,1:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat next to her one time in an auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.81,1:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She was on that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.85,1:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Janice Joplin.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.82,1:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.36,1:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of her name.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.01,1:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.93,1:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to ask a question for my dear friend from Seattle.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.36,1:14:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She was wondering, and her name is Pam,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.30,1:14:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,how lower astral entities,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.30,1:14:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,are they actually part of God, too,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.92,1:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with having non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.75,1:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they God, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.67,1:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.48,1:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are lower astral entities God, as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.56,1:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is God in them?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.25,1:15:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're godless.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.18,1:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're lower astral.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.97,1:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're godless.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.39,1:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're lower astral.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.31,1:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.11,1:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.18,1:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that fit with non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.98,1:15:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that fit?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.52,1:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that fit with non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.72,1:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's got to do with non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.02,1:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.06,1:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.05,1:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.36,1:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the denial of God and divine attributes
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.36,1:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is what gets you to the lower astral.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.35,1:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid love, choose hate,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.26,1:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,choose revenge instead of forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.25,1:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you get to hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.17,1:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.23,1:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell something's evil when they think hell is a great place.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.68,1:16:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stomping.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.43,1:16:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The stomper is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.34,1:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.11,1:16:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just having fun with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.27,1:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for your essences
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.96,1:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and your wonderful gifts of your books and your being.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.56,1:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.10,1:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to you about seven years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.39,1:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and you helped me a lot at that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.65,1:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question now is I had an experience where I was meditating,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.89,1:16:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and there were two triangles that intersected into my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.73,1:16:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and made the shape of the sign of Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.97,1:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the Star of David.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.03,1:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was going to ask you the significance
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.38,1:16:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or the calibration of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.47,1:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.77,1:17:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She was meditating, and she had said
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.60,1:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there was two triangles, you know, in her mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.17,1:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She put her two triangles intercepting into her heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.21,1:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.21,1:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it said, as above, so below.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.64,1:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the words I was given.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.28,1:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.48,1:17:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's wondering what the...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.11,1:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.60,1:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That was over 550, 600, 590.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.27,1:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.53,1:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,590, 580.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.76,1:17:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over 580.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.15,1:17:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over 580.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.52,1:17:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.35,1:17:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.27,1:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nonverbal way of expressing something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.18,1:17:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you want me to express it verbally.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.73,1:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was verbal, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.14,1:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't have come to you that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.07,1:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be verbal instead of nonverbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.22,1:17:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's nonverbal, then it's not supposed to be verbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.10,1:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.14,1:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.81,1:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Verbal anyways, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.50,1:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you verbalize
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.53,1:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,with a nonverbal?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.47,1:18:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.34,1:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.23,1:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.43,1:18:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's why I have so much trouble once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.06,1:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.27,1:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I understand it, but then for verbalizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.67,1:18:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.02,1:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.72,1:18:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.56,1:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.30,1:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.89,1:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.50,1:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.10,1:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.34,1:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you both, and I wanted to thank you, Doc,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.93,1:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for being my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.38,1:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to know if I could just touch your hand
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.64,1:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.82,1:18:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she want now?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.98,1:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.86,1:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Demanding, demanding, demanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.76,1:18:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.06,1:18:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.72,1:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.85,1:18:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.85,1:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.47,1:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've talked to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.22,1:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,about seven years since I last talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.97,1:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very pleased and blessed to be in your presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.78,1:19:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want to thank you from the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.86,1:19:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of us for your work and your service and your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.50,1:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is regarding.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.52,1:19:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pranayama.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.98,1:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've repeatedly calibrated Pranayama at or below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.47,1:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a yoga teacher, and that's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.39,1:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the eight limbs of Patanjali's Yoga Sutras,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.14,1:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which you've calibrated, I believe, in the 700, 740.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.14,1:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.88,1:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you could give me some clarity about why Pranayama,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.18,1:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the fourth limb, is so low.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.94,1:19:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what he's referring to.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.64,1:19:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pranayama.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.03,1:19:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.18,1:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate Pranayama.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.97,1:20:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's that breathing exercise, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.52,1:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a breathing exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.85,1:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.85,1:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 500, calibrates over 495,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.56,1:20:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 350, 380, 340, 350, 350.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.57,1:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of exercises don't calibrate high.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.56,1:20:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.76,1:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, standing on your head, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.81,1:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,probably doesn't calibrate very high.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.97,1:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's yogas based on standing on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.02,1:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.76,1:20:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because yoga is based on every physical form, yes, or activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.81,1:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.32,1:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying it's actually 350 around there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.31,1:20:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,About there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.97,1:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.56,1:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.40,1:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 300.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.40,1:20:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's the same as most Hatha yoga,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.64,1:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,as you've calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.14,1:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, if you're talking about enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.35,1:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't going to get you there at 350, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.72,1:21:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.98,1:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are people attracted to the yogas anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.50,1:21:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.26,1:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.14,1:21:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.43,1:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the kind of we practice, like common in the West?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.82,1:21:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.18,1:21:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The yogas that are common in the West,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.09,1:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,like the physical yoga that most of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.18,1:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, those yogas, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.77,1:21:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see, he's doing physical yoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.90,1:21:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.90,1:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So that all calibrates at about three.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.06,1:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.97,1:21:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 40, 350.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.97,1:21:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.97,1:21:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were practicing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.97,1:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in a positive direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.44,1:21:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.44,1:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, what impresses me about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.09,1:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,about the yogas, is the intention behind it,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.55,1:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,not the yoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.31,1:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I enlightened now?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.51,1:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that 1,000 times, now stop and do it 1,000 times
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.14,1:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I enlightened now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.15,1:22:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it 1,000 times in both directions.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.67,1:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,God feels sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.84,1:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His angels say, there's a guy who's really willing down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.02,1:22:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So then God says, well, give him a pat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.77,1:22:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, boom, boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.81,1:22:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, wow, wow, wow, wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.98,1:22:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It verges into, to my way of thinking, magical.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.47,1:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I breathe this way and stand that way and eat this
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.47,1:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat that, to my way of thinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.53,1:22:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's you're trying to employ the magical.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.97,1:22:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.53,1:22:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.90,1:22:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.27,1:22:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're employing the magical.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.77,1:22:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're employing magic.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.94,1:22:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So a lot of what goes as yoga is just magical thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.94,1:23:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-ha, hoo-ha, boo-hoo, hoo-hoo, yee-hee, ha-ha, hoo-hoo, ha-ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.30,1:23:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I any closer to God than I was?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.60,1:23:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But all action.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.64,1:23:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God's giggling all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.28,1:23:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All action dedicated to God then would take on the level 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.09,1:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.28,1:23:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I dedicate.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.48,1:23:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're doing it out of devotion to God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.65,1:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.56,1:23:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.46,1:23:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.56,1:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.01,1:23:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're doing it out of devotion to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.25,1:23:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's the desire for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.71,1:23:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really have to contemplate
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.31,1:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the correlation between those two things,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.15,1:23:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to God and reaching enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.84,1:23:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you surrender to God, you give up
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.05,1:23:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,working towards enlightenment because now it's up to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.82,1:24:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand the conflict you get into?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.03,1:24:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.77,1:24:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But in resolving the conflict, you find your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.53,1:24:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.14,1:24:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So sacrifice is giving it up to God is always the ultimate path.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.85,1:24:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,God feels sorry for you in the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.48,1:24:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.09,1:24:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.82,1:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had another question for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.89,1:24:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very shy, so she didn't come up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.09,1:24:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But she wanted to know, is it healthy for she raises dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.72,1:24:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to let them sleep with you in your bed?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.84,1:24:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.77,1:24:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it helping to allow dogs to sleep in your bed?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.92,1:24:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.44,1:24:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love the dogs, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.96,1:25:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate the dogs, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.92,1:25:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think loving pets gets you closer to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.56,1:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving pets gets you closer to God, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.89,1:25:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.15,1:25:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your kitties and your doggies and your bunnies
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.50,1:25:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and birdies and chickens and what else we got?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.65,1:25:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.35,1:25:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.14,1:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.77,1:25:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.51,1:25:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.40,1:25:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.55,1:25:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the bird that talks?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.90,1:25:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tucks, what, broccoli?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.85,1:25:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.94,1:25:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call him?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.86,1:25:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he, he's a?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.43,1:25:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,African grey.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.07,1:25:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,African grey parrot, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.22,1:25:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.93,1:25:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an African grey parrot.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.97,1:25:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an African grey parrot.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.64,1:25:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an African grey parrot that is a real knock out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.38,1:25:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.35,1:25:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Says the funniest things unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.69,1:25:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, you know, loving all of God's creations
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.50,1:26:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because I love the elephants, too, and I love the tigers.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.43,1:26:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're all just stunningly beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.93,1:26:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.76,1:26:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am with a group, SCA, Self-Centered Anonymous,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.88,1:26:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that is, you may have heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.92,1:26:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet, well, anyway, they follow your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.53,1:26:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all followers of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.42,1:26:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told them I was coming today,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.35,1:26:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and they wanted to know if you might have something to say to the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.84,1:26:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What group?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.69,1:26:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This group he belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.03,1:26:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.52,1:26:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.73,1:26:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.53,1:26:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.61,1:26:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.65,1:26:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.14,1:26:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you want to become more self-centered?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.47,1:26:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're trying not to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.42,1:26:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.30,1:26:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stop being self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.73,1:26:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.10,1:26:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty self-centered, to want to stop being self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.27,1:27:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The trouble is you're not being self-centered enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.63,1:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it with great intensity, nonstop,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.86,1:27:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll get relieved of it, because you can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.93,1:27:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're asking, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.52,1:27:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's subtle.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.60,1:27:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's subtle.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.89,1:27:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let things be without projecting one's own willfulness into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.69,1:27:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let the world be as it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.56,1:27:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let yourself be as you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.22,1:27:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let others be as they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.77,1:27:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really asking how to surrender to God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.10,1:27:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.31,1:27:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And if...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.60,1:27:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.93,1:27:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.96,1:27:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.02,1:27:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.07,1:27:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.14,1:27:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.19,1:27:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.30,1:27:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.35,1:27:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.42,1:27:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.46,1:27:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.56,1:27:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.57,1:27:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.60,1:27:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're self-centered is where you're at with it,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.30,1:27:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then you surrender to God that you're self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.61,1:27:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.68,1:27:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.86,1:28:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a sin?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.89,1:28:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
