Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.89,1:33:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.23,1:33:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time, Karen.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.73,1:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't keep up with the current scandal
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.96,1:34:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of various former teachers.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.10,1:34:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, but that was the one that...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.96,1:34:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.76,1:34:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll take...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.73,1:34:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When do we...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.07,1:34:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.15,1:34:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my thing's off.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.22,1:34:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you fell from grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.56,1:34:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.10,1:34:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.22,1:34:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My watch is...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.30,1:34:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with my watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.23,1:34:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.56,1:34:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.22,1:34:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with overcoming karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.42,1:34:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have Renard's.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.96,1:34:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where your hands get really cold
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.84,1:34:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the fingers will turn white in the cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.42,1:34:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And through kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.85,1:34:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it was identified as a past life expression of ancient karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.77,1:34:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if the undoing of that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.88,1:34:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is through prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.00,1:34:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and also you answered another question about karma
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.23,1:34:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and undoing bad karma with good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.89,1:35:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thought that immediately came to my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.26,1:35:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,was for me to volunteer at a hospice because I...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.23,1:35:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be good, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.57,1:35:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.10,1:35:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be good.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.47,1:35:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.21,1:35:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's talking about what I used to have.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.28,1:35:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.05,1:35:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Renard.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.59,1:35:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Renard syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.63,1:35:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.55,1:35:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.14,1:35:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Renos.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.67,1:35:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Renos disease, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.77,1:35:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.94,1:35:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would be perfect, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.64,1:35:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.40,1:35:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.93,1:35:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.67,1:35:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.77,1:35:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.61,1:35:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.38,1:35:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I used to have to wear gloves in the...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.63,1:35:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to wear gloves even in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.94,1:35:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I related it one time
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.02,1:35:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,going to a Chinese restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.47,1:35:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and eating with chopsticks with my gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.10,1:36:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.64,1:36:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.97,1:36:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.27,1:36:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You previously stated that you can only go as high
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.89,1:36:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as you have gone low.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.78,1:36:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you speak and say more about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.27,1:36:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.38,1:36:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.68,1:36:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hypothetically true.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.52,1:36:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it can vary from individual to individual.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.36,1:36:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If a person hits the depths, they despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.63,1:36:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you tell them there's a benefit to that,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.52,1:36:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a benefit,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.19,1:36:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you've looked at things
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.18,1:36:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that you otherwise couldn't have handled
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.96,1:36:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or couldn't have looked at,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.25,1:36:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've now earned the right to transcend them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.72,1:36:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's like a karmic benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.47,1:36:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to have looked at the darkest,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.07,1:36:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,been through the worst,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.56,1:37:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you've still maintained your allegiance to God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.32,1:37:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and truth and love and divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.13,1:37:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've earned the karmic right to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.93,1:37:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's sort of a saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.85,1:37:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only be as high as...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.72,1:37:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You once were low.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.47,1:37:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's karmically often true.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.32,1:37:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's karmically often true.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.15,1:37:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.77,1:37:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.39,1:37:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an individual matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.84,1:37:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In an individual matter, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.60,1:37:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.51,1:37:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this will be the last question.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.39,1:37:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.30,1:37:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.02,1:37:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.77,1:37:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.02,1:37:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.15,1:37:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You got one last cookie you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.61,1:37:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One last quick question or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.19,1:37:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.03,1:37:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.73,1:37:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do a closing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.89,1:37:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a prayer sent.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.93,1:37:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.22,1:37:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like us all to pray for Japan
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.57,1:38:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people that are suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.23,1:38:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.39,1:38:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.31,1:38:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.77,1:38:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all join together
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.81,1:38:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to offset what's going on currently in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.52,1:38:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll have to lead the prayer on this
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.98,1:38:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was your thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.44,1:38:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.43,1:38:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.89,1:38:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the mic?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.01,1:38:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.32,1:38:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.17,1:38:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.56,1:38:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.52,1:38:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.76,1:38:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No flies on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.75,1:38:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.22,1:38:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I on?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.76,1:38:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.92,1:38:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all of us to do a silent prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.03,1:38:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for the people in Japan that are suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.93,1:38:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently had a lovely lady from our group
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.50,1:38:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that has crossed over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.02,1:39:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So if everyone could say a prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.46,1:39:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for these people that are now making the transition,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.69,1:39:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we appreciate it very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.39,1:39:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.72,1:39:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could just do a silent prayer for those people,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.93,1:39:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.72,1:39:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for thy love and forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.31,1:39:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to heal the sorrow and the pain and the suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.89,1:39:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of people who are caught in that catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.11,1:39:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and that their suffering may lead to serve thee.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.68,1:39:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.06,1:39:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.98,1:39:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you want to go ahead and bless everyone that's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.93,1:39:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so grateful for all of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.14,1:39:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you have come quite a long distance to be with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.85,1:39:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And we appreciate it so much
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.09,1:39:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,because without you, the work would be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.86,1:40:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And we are so appreciative of all of you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.14,1:40:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,showing up for the events.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.27,1:40:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It touches both of our hearts very deeply.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.77,1:40:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank thee, O Lord, for thy divine blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.09,1:40:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,upon this group of people here assembled this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.76,1:40:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We give thanks for thy presence, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.48,1:40:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.27,1:40:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we hug each other and bless each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.72,1:40:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the part I always like.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.01,1:40:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best part of the whole show.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.36,1:40:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Big hug and God love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.72,1:40:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these beautiful flowers on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.77,1:40:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody sent us these gorgeous flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.97,1:40:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, they're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.02,1:40:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.52,1:41:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Lidart.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.81,1:41:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I got a mic on now?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.89,1:41:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.93,1:41:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the mic?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.27,1:41:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.51,1:41:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a microphone attached to my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.00,1:41:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.00,1:41:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know I had a microphone attached to my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.85,1:41:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and rush this little microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.14,1:41:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's God's microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.22,1:41:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.89,1:41:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had a lovely day.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.64,1:41:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely day to be here again with you this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.53,1:41:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love is a blessing to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.14,1:41:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When the love of this group is sent
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.02,1:42:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to the people in trouble in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.50,1:42:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually has,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.02,1:42:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually has an effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.02,1:42:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually has a literal,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.56,1:42:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,real effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.56,1:42:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.56,1:42:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.56,1:42:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.56,1:42:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.56,1:42:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.67,1:42:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That had a literal,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.80,1:42:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,physical effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.80,1:42:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.80,1:42:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.92,1:42:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.92,1:42:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this microphone still on?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.92,1:42:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just love that old doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.89,1:42:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also a sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.89,1:42:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.89,1:43:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Docky Dock.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.40,1:43:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a kiss, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.40,1:43:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.40,1:43:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.65,1:43:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.65,1:43:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.75,1:43:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.28,1:43:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.28,1:43:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.60,1:43:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.60,1:43:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
